item.title: Automating Machine Learning Pipelines with GPT Engineer
item.description: GPT Engineer is a new tool that allows automating the creation of machine learning pipelines by leveraging the power of large language models like GPT-3. It interacts via conversational prompts and clarifying questions to generate full code solutions split across modular files.
